properties.areaDesc: Coastal waters from Okaloosa-Walton County Line to Pensacola FL out 20 NM; Waters from Okaloosa-Walton County Line to Pensacola FL from 20 to 60 NM
properties.headline: Small Craft Advisory issued January 23 at 3:56AM CST until January 23 at 9:00PM CST by NWS Mobile AL
properties.description:
* WHAT...Southeast winds 15 to 25 kt expected.

* WHERE...Coastal waters from Okaloosa Walton County Line FL to
Pensacola FL out 20 NM and Waters from Okaloosa Walton County
Line FL to Pensacola FL from 20 to 60 NM.

* WHEN...Until 9 PM CST this evening.

* IMPACTS...Conditions will be hazardous to small craft.
properties.instruction:
Inexperienced mariners, especially those operating smaller
vessels, should avoid navigating in hazardous conditions.

NWSheadline: SMALL CRAFT ADVISORY IN EFFECT UNTIL 9 PM CST THIS EVENING
